 align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding:22px 32px 0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:22px;line-height:24px;font-family:&quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#1f3d2e;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">{{{organization_name}}}</p><p style="font-size:10px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8a6a3f;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Reports · 5 of 7</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="padding:8px 32px 32px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:30px;line-height:1.05;font-family:&quot;Cormorant Garamond&quot;, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.015em;color:#1a1a18;margin:14px 0 18px;margin-top:14px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:18px;margin-left:0">Your reports.</p><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#3a3a36;margin:0 0 14px;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0">{{{recipient_name}}}<!-- --> — reporting is the part of the relationship you will return to most, so it has a page of its own rather than being buried in a folder tree.</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="border:1px solid rgba(26,26,24,0.10);padding:18px;margin:8px 0 22px;background-color:#fbf9f4"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:10px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8a6a3f;margin:0;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">How it is organised</p><div><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a18;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Grouped by fund</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:3px 0 0;margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">Each fund you hold gets its own section. Reports that apply to the whole firm are grouped as Firm-wide.</p></div><div><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgba(26,26,24,0.10);border-top-width:1px;margin:14px 0"/><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a18;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">The latest is surfaced first</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:3px 0 0;margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">The most recent report for each fund sits at the top with its publication date, ready to view or download.</p></div><div><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgba(26,26,24,0.10);border-top-width:1px;margin:14px 0"/><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a18;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">The history sits beneath it</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:3px 0 0;margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0">Every earlier report stays available, newest first. Nothing is retired when a new quarter is published.</p></div></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="border-left:2px solid #b8915c;padding:2px 0 2px 14px;margin:0 0 22px"><tbody><tr><td><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color:#6f6e68;margin:0;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Reports are also filed in Documents alongside everything else shared with you. This page is the reading view; Documents is the record.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="text-align:center;margin:18px 0 4px"><tbody><tr><td><a href="{{{app_url}}}" style="line-height:100%;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;mso-padding-alt:0px;background-color:#1f3d2e;color:#ffffff;padding:12px 22px;border-radius:2px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;padding-top:12px;padding-right:22px;padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:22px" target="_blank"><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:366.66666666666663%;mso-text-raise:18" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;</i><![endif]--></span><span style="max-width:100%;display:inline-block;line-height:120%;mso-padding-alt:0px;mso-text-raise:9px">Read your latest report</span><span><!--[if mso]><i style="mso-font-width:366.66666666666663%" hidden>&#8202;&#8202;&#8202;&#8203;</i><![endif]--></span></a></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:rgba(26,26,24,0.10);margin:28px 0 14px"/><p style="font-size:10px;line-height:24px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter Tight&quot;, -apple-system, Helvetica, Arial, sans-s